subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: Camille Little had 17 points and 13 rebounds, Sue Bird scored 12 points, and the short-handed Seattle Storm rallied to win their sixth straight game, 65-58 over the Liberty on Tuesday night at Madison Square Garden.
